{
  "texts": [
    "Median sample size across all included RCTs was 186 (IQR 56-654).",
    "Most RCTs were single centre (n = 39, 60%) versus multicentre (n = 26, 40%).",
    "Studies were commonly unblinded (n = 24, 37%) or singleblinded (n = 21, 32%), with few double-blinded RCTs (n = 2, 3%).",
    "18 (28%) did not report details of any blinding.",
    "The most common types of AI intervention were endoscopy assistance (n = 13, 20%), image enhancement (n = 11, 17%), image classification (n = 9, 14%), and chatbots (n = 7, 11%)."
  ]
}